41struct re_s *
42ldap_pvt_runqueue_insert(
43 struct runqueue_s* rq,
44 time_t interval,
45 ldap_pvt_thread_start_t *routine,
46 void *arg,
47 char *tname,
48 char *tspec
49)
50{
51 struct re_s* entry;
52
53 entry = (struct re_s *) LDAP_CALLOC( 1, sizeof( struct re_s ));
54 if ( entry ) {
55 entry->interval.tv_sec = interval;
56 entry->interval.tv_usec = 0;
57 entry->next_sched.tv_sec = time( NULL );
58 entry->next_sched.tv_usec = 0;
59 entry->routine = routine;
60 entry->arg = arg;
61 entry->tname = tname;
62 entry->tspec = tspec;
63 LDAP_STAILQ_INSERT_HEAD( &rq->task_list, entry, tnext );
64 }
65 return entry;
66}
67
68struct re_s *
69ldap_pvt_runqueue_find(
70 struct runqueue_s *rq,
71 ldap_pvt_thread_start_t *routine,
72 void *arg
73)
74{
75 struct re_s* e;
76
77 LDAP_STAILQ_FOREACH( e, &rq->task_list, tnext ) {
78 if ( e->routine == routine && e->arg == arg )
79 return e;
80 }
81 return NULL;
82}
83
84void
85ldap_pvt_runqueue_remove(
86 struct runqueue_s* rq,
87 struct re_s* entry
88)
89{
90 struct re_s* e;
91
92 LDAP_STAILQ_FOREACH( e, &rq->task_list, tnext ) {
93 if ( e == entry)
94 break;
95 }
96
97 assert( e == entry );
98
99 LDAP_STAILQ_REMOVE( &rq->task_list, entry, re_s, tnext );
100
101 LDAP_FREE( entry );
102}
103
104struct re_s*
105ldap_pvt_runqueue_next_sched(
106 struct runqueue_s* rq,
107 struct timeval* next_run
108)
109{
110 struct re_s* entry;
111
112 entry = LDAP_STAILQ_FIRST( &rq->task_list );
113 if ( entry == NULL || entry->next_sched.tv_sec == 0 ) {
114 return NULL;
115 } else {
116 *next_run = entry->next_sched;
117 return entry;
118 }
119}
120
121void
122ldap_pvt_runqueue_runtask(
123 struct runqueue_s* rq,
124 struct re_s* entry
125)
126{
127 LDAP_STAILQ_INSERT_TAIL( &rq->run_list, entry, rnext );
128}
129
130void
131ldap_pvt_runqueue_stoptask(
132 struct runqueue_s* rq,
133 struct re_s* entry
134)
135{
136 LDAP_STAILQ_REMOVE( &rq->run_list, entry, re_s, rnext );
137}
138
139int
140ldap_pvt_runqueue_isrunning(
141 struct runqueue_s* rq,
142 struct re_s* entry
143)
144{
145 struct re_s* e;
146
147 LDAP_STAILQ_FOREACH( e, &rq->run_list, rnext ) {
148 if ( e == entry ) {
149 return 1;
150 }
151 }
152 return 0;
153}
154
155void
156ldap_pvt_runqueue_resched(
157 struct runqueue_s* rq,
158 struct re_s* entry,
159 int defer
160)
161{
162 struct re_s* prev;
163 struct re_s* e;
164
165 LDAP_STAILQ_FOREACH( e, &rq->task_list, tnext ) {
166 if ( e == entry )
167 break;
168 }
169
170 assert ( e == entry );
171
172 LDAP_STAILQ_REMOVE( &rq->task_list, entry, re_s, tnext );
173
174 if ( !defer ) {
175 entry->next_sched.tv_sec = time( NULL ) + entry->interval.tv_sec;
176 } else {
177 entry->next_sched.tv_sec = 0;
178 }
179
180 if ( LDAP_STAILQ_EMPTY( &rq->task_list )) {
181 LDAP_STAILQ_INSERT_HEAD( &rq->task_list, entry, tnext );
182 } else if ( entry->next_sched.tv_sec == 0 ) {
183 LDAP_STAILQ_INSERT_TAIL( &rq->task_list, entry, tnext );
184 } else {
185 prev = NULL;
186 LDAP_STAILQ_FOREACH( e, &rq->task_list, tnext ) {
187 if ( e->next_sched.tv_sec == 0 ) {
188 if ( prev == NULL ) {
189 LDAP_STAILQ_INSERT_HEAD( &rq->task_list, entry, tnext );
190 } else {
191 LDAP_STAILQ_INSERT_AFTER( &rq->task_list, prev, entry, tnext );
192 }
193 return;
194 } else if ( e->next_sched.tv_sec > entry->next_sched.tv_sec ) {
195 if ( prev == NULL ) {
196 LDAP_STAILQ_INSERT_HEAD( &rq->task_list, entry, tnext );
197 } else {
198 LDAP_STAILQ_INSERT_AFTER( &rq->task_list, prev, entry, tnext );
199 }
200 return;
201 }
202 prev = e;
203 }
204 LDAP_STAILQ_INSERT_TAIL( &rq->task_list, entry, tnext );
205 }
206}
207
208int
209ldap_pvt_runqueue_persistent_backload(
210 struct runqueue_s* rq
211)
212{
213 struct re_s* e;
214 int count = 0;
215
216 ldap_pvt_thread_mutex_lock( &rq->rq_mutex );
217 if ( !LDAP_STAILQ_EMPTY( &rq->task_list )) {
218 LDAP_STAILQ_FOREACH( e, &rq->task_list, tnext ) {
219 if ( e->next_sched.tv_sec == 0 )
220 count++;
221 }
222 }
223 ldap_pvt_thread_mutex_unlock( &rq->rq_mutex );
224 return count;
225}
